<p>Dr <b>Patrick Dixon</b> is a business thinker and <a href="/wiki/Futurist" title="Futurist">futurist</a>. His Web TV site <sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> has more than 11 million unique users. He is Chairman of Global Change Ltd,<sup id="cite_ref-t50_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-t50-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup> author of twelve books (485,000 printed in 23 languages) including <i><a href="/wiki/Futurewise" title="Futurewise">Futurewise</a></i> and <i><a href="/wiki/Building_a_Better_Business" title="Building a Better Business">Building a Better Business</a></i>, has spoken to audiences in 50 nations, has given hundreds of radio and TV interviews on major issues and trends, and has been ranked as one of the 20 most influential business thinkers alive today.<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2" title=""><span>[</span>3<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
