<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.globalchange.com/financialtimesdixonfeature31oct2005.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.globalchange.com/financialtimesdixonfeature31oct2005.pdf" rel="nofollow">Wake up to stronger tribes and a longer life</a> - Financial Times</li>
